The paper deals with the application of convolutional neural networks for image classification, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep learning models such as ResNet, Inception, VGG, and AlexNet suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL).
